  "body": "# Problem\r\n\r\nThe current implementation to reply to a contact verification request is using the old component `quo.core/text-input`, but the redesign requires a new multiline component. At the time of implementation of the identity verification flow, the new component wasn't available.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/46027/201723774-8610931c-4db3-446b-b859-04ad2aba34aa.png\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n### Expected\r\n\r\nOnce the new text input component is available, we should use it. See the specs here https://www.figma.com/file/WQZcp6S0EnzxdTL4taoKDv/Design-System?node-id=57%3A5646\r\n\r\n<img height=\"500\" alt=\"Reply\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/46027/201732743-30e7e398-1284-4dda-bab1-752c13e563ac.png\">\r\n",
