    "body": "Also as have been [agreed](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/15284#issuecomment-1466203855) with @ilmotta the following issue will be addressed within current ticket:\r\n\r\n### Keyboard overlaps Identity verification bottom sheet\r\n\r\n**Steps:** \r\n\r\n1. Generate identity verification request for User B\r\n2. By User B: open AC => tap identity verification notification => make answer input field active to open keyboard\r\n3. See if keyboard overlaps Identity verification bottom sheet\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** Keyboard overlaps Identity verification bottom sheet\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/224648435-72ea9ea5-c36c-49c4-8b32-17e78304682e.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n",
